          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>ModernTimez was born from a simple idea: finding the perfect gift should be a joy, not a chore. We curate modern, thoughtful gifts for every person and every occasion — from birthdays to weddings, holidays to \"just because\" moments.</p>"
