        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We started ModernTimez Gift Shop because we were tired of gifting the same generic candles and gift sets. Every product in our collection is hand-selected for quality, uniqueness, and that \"wow\" factor that makes a gift truly memorable.</p><p>From sleek home accessories to personalized keepsakes, our range spans every budget and every taste. Whether you're shopping for your best friend, your boss, or someone who \"has everything\" — we've got something that will make them smile.</p>"
