          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Carefully Curated",
            "text": "<p>Every item in our store is hand-picked by our team. We test, assess, and select only products that we'd be proud to give to the people we love.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "col-2": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Modern & Unique",
            "text": "<p>We stay ahead of trends to bring you gifts that feel fresh and contemporary — never generic, never forgettable. Find things here that you won't find at the mall.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "col-3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Always Memorable",
            "text": "<p>The best gifts are ones that people remember years later. We focus on items with lasting value — things that are used, displayed, or treasured long after the wrapping paper is gone.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
      },
